    "name": "Drepanaspis",
    "description": "Perhaps the greatest catch to be found at Grymm & Enid, the drepanaspis is so rare that, until now, no one was sure that one <span class=\"emphasis\">could</span> be found at Grymm & Enid.<br><br>[Suitable for printing on large canvases.]",
